{"tid":980151,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"華納即將推出《真人快打》動畫電影，不改 R 級暴力本色血流成河","createTime":"2019-01-13T09:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T00:21:23.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbdfbaef6b53990219852274d6380af7a996939","tid":980151,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86598/5c3ad40f89833.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86598%2F5c3ad40f89833.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=0b76af10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在現在漫威、 DC 英雄電影、電視劇當道的時候，想要殺出一條血路實在是不容易，知名的華納公司即將搬出經典電玩作品《真人快打》（Mortal Kombat）改編的動畫電影，並且不改原本 R 級血腥暴力的特色，將在影音串流平台下架，勾起了許多資深電玩迷的回憶，是否可以成功創下佳績？大家都在看。<br />\n《真人快打》（Mortal Kombat）是電玩公司 Midway 1992 年首次發表的格鬥電玩遊戲，在當時最大的特色就是血腥暴力的設定，造成不小的轟動。陸續翻拍了電影《魔宮帝國》（1995年）、《魔宮帝國2》（1997年）、《魔宮帝國：重生》（2010年），以及電視劇等作品，讓這樣的故事世界觀持續延續。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0dz0YU0jJr4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0dz0YU0jJr4&d=bgVAGvIKTpLDxAMLclI%2B7v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=19028269\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0dz0YU0jJr4</a><br />\n而這次重啟動畫電影也將請來原本人馬的配音卡司， Steve Blum （角色Sub-Zer）和 Patrick Seitz（角色 Scorpion）的配音員，絕對會讓當時的電玩迷再次回味。另外確定《夢魘殺魔》（Dexter）女主角 Jennifer Carpenter，以及 DC 影集《逐星女》（Star Girl）的 Joel McHale 兩位女星也都將參與，讓人更加期待。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.juksy.com/archives/81769?atl=1&amp;gp=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.juksy.com%2Farchives%2F81769%3Fatl%3D1%26gp%3D4&d=bgVAGvIKTpLDxAMLclI%2B7v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=215783f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.juksy.com/archives/81769?atl=1&amp;gp=4</a>"},{"pid":"fc91af56ac5fd26991a8aa373b41edd52da6d63c","tid":980151,"uid":177590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"Finish him!"},{"pid":"3f4b74a72bc76517ae64fb82d8aed98b6aeff226","tid":980151,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"R級動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a414a50886044398da0feecbd023d7765c0f9f","tid":980151,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"溫子仁,We trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46d1572795217e95fc16b80a5f976ab73649d1c","tid":980151,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc91af56ac5fd26991a8aa373b41edd52da6d63c","tid":980151,"uid":177590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"Finish him!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"Finish her!"},{"pid":"3b303b90b5f12c83938385922524ae67b161532b","tid":980151,"uid":127075,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:30:45.000Z","msg":"雖然隻game幾好玩，但不得不說d角色造型真係不討好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89dab3e7d59fb5eb1e561c32c1501abb7cd1671","tid":980151,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446e3890690fa97af05f0c4a4efb8598f9c4f6ef","tid":980151,"uid":51041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"sonya<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cebcc9aa5bd2e1751fcfbb32752061ac2ceeded","tid":980151,"uid":179283,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:28:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>Fatality!</strong>"},{"pid":"a3b722c643f3ecf5ebf8e96709aec2516286ab8e","tid":980151,"uid":60133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco